translated:
Yngwe, Sven Ture Konrad, parish priest, Valdemarsvik, born on 15/3/02 in Fivelstad, Östergötland. Son of Sven Y. and Ida Ljungquist. Married on 31/\d\d to Brita Gjörling. Children: Ulla and Kerstin (born in 1931), Sven (born in 1933), Mats (born in 1939). 

Education: Examined in Lund in 1922, Bachelor of Theology in 1925, Theological Candidate in 1930. Practical theological exam and ordained as a priest of Linköping Diocese in 1931.

Career: Assistant pastor in Västra Ny in 1931, in Vireda in 1932, pastor at the central prison in Mariestad in the same year, assistant pastor in Adelöv in 1934. Became parish priest there in 1935 before transferring to Valdemarsvik in 1944. 

Involvement: Chairman of the church assembly in Adelöv from 1935 to 1944, member of the municipal council from 1939 to 1944, municipal board member in 1944, school board member from 1935 to 1944. In Valdemarsvik, chairman of the church council since 1944, school board member since 1945, child welfare board member since 1944, lecturer in various associations and library board member since 1944, member of the Valdemarsvik Parish Foundation.
